    <h3>b. Device Permissions and Usage</h3>
    <p>To provide full functionality, our app requests the following permissions:</p>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Permission</th>
        <th>Purpose</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE / WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE</td>
