      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>CAMERA / CAMERA.AUTOfocus</td>
        <td>Used for scanning product barcodes, QR codes, and capturing item photos within the app.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>GET_ACCOUNTS</td>
        <td>Used for retrieving your registered Google account to simplify login or backup processes.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
